name: Basic Shoots
description: I am not the wedding photographer for couples looking for a fairy tale. I am not the wedding photographer for couples looking for a light and airy dreamscape or a day that feels like a photo shoot. I'm the wedding photographer for you if you value moments and the beauty of your everyday life.

name: Creative Shoots
description: I am a professional wedding photographer from Bangladesh.I try to tell stories with my photographs.I believe my photographs should hold the power to bring memories to life even after years.

name: Creative with Edit
description: I just love to click, never feel tired while clicking. This affection helped me to jump into professional field as a wedding & fashion photographer. I need to learn many more things in order to do something different in this vast world.

name: Creative with Edit & Outdoor
description: Being a photographer is probably the finest pleasure I've ever owned from life. This satisfaction always pushes me to take breathtaking photographs.
